	<p pid="b.14.2/1">The Town and Country Planning (Major Infrastructure Project Inquiries Procedure) (England) Rules 2005 (SI 2005/2115) only came into force on <phrase class="date" code="2005-08-24">24 August</phrase>. Supporting guidance was issued in ODPM Circular 07/2005 which states the new arrangements will be monitored over a five year period and if necessary changes will be considered.</p>
