	<p pid="b.15.6/18">Note:</p>
	<p pid="b.15.6/19">The term &quot;self-inflicted death&quot; is employed rather than suicide. This includes, all those deaths where it appears the person may have acted specifically to take his/her own life and not only those that receive a &quot;suicide&quot; verdict at inquest.</p>
</reply>
